<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="give-up">give up</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>认输；放弃；让：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is difficult to give up smoking.
戒烟可不容易。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She decided to give up her job and start a coffee bar.
她决定辞去工作，开一家咖啡馆。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>gave up</strong> his seat <strong>to</strong> a pregnant woman.
他把座位让给了一位孕妇。</p></div></div>